r2569 | jcbowman | 2007-06-18 19:59:33 +0200 (Mon, 18 Jun 2007) | 11 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/graph.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain_picture.asy
