r1874 | jcbowman | 2006-10-07 22:00:36 +0200 (Sat, 07 Oct 2006) | 8 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain_Label.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain_filldraw.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain_pens.asy
