r307 | jcbowman | 2005-02-04 23:15:16 +0100 (Fri, 04 Feb 2005) | 9 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/feynman.asy
   A /trunk/asymptote/base/patterns.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain.asy
