r270 | jcbowman | 2005-01-26 09:14:32 +0100 (Wed, 26 Jan 2005) | 9 lines
Changed paths:
   A /trunk/asymptote/base/babel.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/math.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/base/plain.asy
   M /trunk/asymptote/camp.l
